SQL: SELECT avg("lineorder"."lo_revenue") as agg_0 FROM "lineorder"  WHERE CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) LIKE '%AI%R%' OR CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) LIKE '%TRUCK%';

SELECT "customer"."c_mktsegment", "customer"."c_city", max("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0, max("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_1 FROM "customer"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%EUROPE%' AND "customer"."c_custkey" >= 9682 AND CAST("customer"."c_nation" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%RUSS%IA%' GROUP BY "customer"."c_mktsegment", "customer"."c_city" ORDER BY "customer"."c_mktsegment", "customer"."c_city";

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_linenumber", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "part" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "lineorder"."lo_partkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "lineorder"."lo_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"  WHERE "part"."p_type" = 'SMALL BURNISHED BRASS' AND "part"."p_color" IN ('misty', 'frosted', 'firebrick', 'floral', 'royal', 'cornsilk', 'cornflower', 'seashell', 'ghost', 'blush', 'lemon', 'orange', 'chiffon', 'gainsboro') GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_linenumber" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_linenumber";

SELECT "supplier"."s_suppkey", "supplier"."s_city", sum("supplier"."s_suppkey") as agg_0 FROM "supplier"  WHERE CAST("supplier"."s_nation" AS varchar) LIKE '%JORDAN%' GROUP BY "supplier"."s_suppkey", "supplier"."s_city" ORDER BY "supplier"."s_suppkey", "supplier"."s_city";

SELECT "customer"."c_city", max("lineorder"."lo_tax" + "lineorder"."lo_extendedprice") as agg_0, min("part"."p_size") as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM "part" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "lineorder"."lo_partkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "lineorder"."lo_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"  WHERE "lineorder"."lo_shipmode" = 'TRUCK' GROUP BY "customer"."c_city" ORDER BY "customer"."c_city";

SELECT max("lineorder"."lo_discount") as agg_0, max("lineorder"."lo_supplycost") as agg_1 FROM "lineorder" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "lineorder"."lo_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"  WHERE "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" = '2-HIGH' AND "customer"."c_mktsegment" IN ('MACHINERY', 'FURNITURE', 'HOUSEHOLD', 'AUTOMOBILE') AND (CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) LIKE '%F%OB%' OR "lineorder"."lo_shipmode" = 'REG AIR' OR CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%FOB%') AND "lineorder"."lo_partkey" >= 149404;

SELECT "supplier"."s_suppkey", "lineorder"."lo_discount", COUNT(*) as agg_0, avg("lineorder"."lo_tax" + "lineorder"."lo_suppkey") as agg_1 FROM "supplier" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "lineorder"."lo_suppkey"  WHERE "lineorder"."lo_ordertotalprice" BETWEEN 13756952 AND 15682723 GROUP BY "supplier"."s_suppkey", "lineorder"."lo_discount" ORDER BY "supplier"."s_suppkey", "lineorder"."lo_discount";

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_orderdate", "lineorder"."lo_quantity", avg("lineorder"."lo_quantity" + "lineorder"."lo_supplycost") as agg_0 FROM "supplier" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "lineorder"."lo_suppkey"  WHERE CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) LIKE '%MA%IL%' AND "supplier"."s_region" = 'AMERICA' AND ("supplier"."s_suppkey" >= 110 OR "supplier"."s_suppkey" <= 1197) AND "supplier"."s_city" = 'BRAZIL   9' AND "lineorder"."lo_custkey" BETWEEN 31185 AND 35716 GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_orderdate", "lineorder"."lo_quantity" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_orderdate", "lineorder"."lo_quantity";

SELECT "customer"."c_nation", avg("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0, min("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_1, min("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_2 FROM "customer"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_city" AS varchar) LIKE '%INDI%A%' AND CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%MACH%INERY%' AND (CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) LIKE '%EUROPE%' OR "customer"."c_region" IN ('EUROPE', 'AFRICA') OR CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%EAST%') AND CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%AMER%ICA%' GROUP BY "customer"."c_nation" ORDER BY "customer"."c_nation";
SELECT sum("part"."p_partkey") as agg_0 FROM "part"  WHERE "part"."p_type" != 'LARGE ANODIZED TIN';

SELECT sum("lineorder"."lo_tax") as agg_0, sum("lineorder"."lo_supplycost") as agg_1 FROM "lineorder" LEFT OUTER JOIN "supplier" ON "lineorder"."lo_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "lineorder"."lo_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_city" AS varchar) LIKE '%SAUD%I%' AND CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) LIKE '%MAIL%' AND CAST("supplier"."s_nation" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%KINGDOM%' AND CAST("supplier"."s_region" AS varchar) LIKE '%EA%ST%';

SELECT min("supplier"."s_suppkey") as agg_0, min("supplier"."s_suppkey") as agg_1 FROM "supplier"  WHERE CAST("supplier"."s_nation" AS varchar) LIKE '%ROM%ANIA%' AND CAST("supplier"."s_city" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%FR%ANCE%';

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_linenumber", max("lineorder"."lo_discount" + "lineorder"."lo_commitdate") as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM "lineorder" LEFT OUTER JOIN "supplier" ON "lineorder"."lo_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey"  WHERE "supplier"."s_region" IN ('AMERICA', 'AFRICA', 'EUROPE') AND "lineorder"."lo_shippriority" <= 0 AND "lineorder"."lo_quantity" != 38 AND (CAST("supplier"."s_city" AS varchar) LIKE '%CHINA%' OR CAST("supplier"."s_city" AS varchar) LIKE '%JORDAN%' OR "supplier"."s_city" != 'IRAN     8') GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_linenumber" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_linenumber";

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_shippriority", sum("lineorder"."lo_ordertotalprice" + "lineorder"."lo_discount") as agg_0, min("lineorder"."lo_suppkey") as agg_1, avg("lineorder"."lo_extendedprice" + "lineorder"."lo_supplycost") as agg_2 FROM "supplier" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "lineorder"."lo_suppkey"  WHERE CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%MA%IL%' AND ("supplier"."s_region" IN ('AMERICA', 'ASIA', 'MIDDLE EAST', 'EUROPE') OR ("supplier"."s_phone" = '21-659-826-9095' AND "supplier"."s_region" != 'EUROPE')) GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_shippriority" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_shippriority";

SELECT min("lineorder"."lo_custkey") as agg_0, avg("lineorder"."lo_discount") as agg_1 FROM "lineorder" LEFT OUTER JOIN "part" ON "lineorder"."lo_partkey" = "part"."p_partkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "supplier" ON "lineorder"."lo_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "lineorder"."lo_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"  WHERE ("part"."p_container" IN ('JUMBO JAR', 'MED BAG', 'LG DRUM', 'JUMBO PKG', 'LG BOX', 'JUMBO CAN', 'WRAP BAG', 'MED PKG', 'LG PKG', 'JUMBO BAG', 'LG CASE', 'WRAP BOX', 'MED PACK', 'MED JAR', 'MED BOX', 'WRAP JAR', 'JUMBO PACK', 'SM BAG', 'LG BAG', 'SM CASE', 'SM DRUM') OR "part"."p_name" = 'deep light') AND CAST("part"."p_container" AS varchar) LIKE '%L%G%' AND "lineorder"."lo_suppkey" <= 2216 AND "part"."p_category" IN ('MFGR#15', 'MFGR#34', 'MFGR#13', 'MFGR#25', 'MFGR#42', 'MFGR#41', 'MFGR#31', 'MFGR#43', 'MFGR#11', 'MFGR#14', 'MFGR#32', 'MFGR#12', 'MFGR#44', 'MFGR#35', 'MFGR#54', 'MFGR#21', 'MFGR#55', 'MFGR#24', 'MFGR#45', 'MFGR#52', 'MFGR#33');

SELECT "customer"."c_city", "customer"."c_nation", min("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM "customer"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%E%UROPE%' AND CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%FURN%ITURE%' AND "customer"."c_custkey" <= 39580 GROUP BY "customer"."c_city", "customer"."c_nation" ORDER BY "customer"."c_city", "customer"."c_nation";

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_linenumber", "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority", max("lineorder"."lo_supplycost") as agg_0, max("lineorder"."lo_shippriority" + "customer"."c_custkey") as agg_1 FROM "part" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "lineorder"."lo_partkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "lineorder"."lo_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"  WHERE "part"."p_color" IN ('blanched', 'violet', 'navy', 'saddle', 'beige', 'pink', 'drab', 'misty', 'azure', 'orchid', 'navajo', 'white', 'burnished') AND CAST("part"."p_name" AS varchar) LIKE '%s%andy%' AND "lineorder"."lo_shipmode" = 'RAIL' AND "part"."p_type" = 'STANDARD BURNISHED BRASS' AND "customer"."c_mktsegment" IN ('AUTOMOBILE', 'MACHINERY') GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_linenumber", "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_linenumber", "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority";

SELECT "supplier"."s_suppkey", sum("lineorder"."lo_tax" + "lineorder"."lo_quantity") as agg_0, avg("lineorder"."lo_partkey" + "lineorder"."lo_supplycost") as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM "lineorder" LEFT OUTER JOIN "part" ON "lineorder"."lo_partkey" = "part"."p_partkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "supplier" ON "lineorder"."lo_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey"  WHERE "supplier"."s_nation" = 'MOZAMBIQUE' AND "part"."p_category" = 'MFGR#35' AND "lineorder"."lo_linenumber" <= 2 GROUP BY "supplier"."s_suppkey" ORDER BY "supplier"."s_suppkey";

SELECT sum("lineorder"."lo_orderdate") as agg_0, max("lineorder"."lo_shippriority") as agg_1 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "lineorder"."lo_custkey"  WHERE CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) LIKE '%AI%R%';

SELECT "customer"."c_mktsegment", "lineorder"."lo_quantity", min("lineorder"."lo_quantity") as agg_0, avg("lineorder"."lo_supplycost" + "lineorder"."lo_orderkey") as agg_1 FROM "lineorder" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "lineorder"."lo_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"  WHERE "customer"."c_region" IN ('AMERICA', 'AFRICA') AND "lineorder"."lo_discount" != 7 AND "customer"."c_mktsegment" = 'FURNITURE' AND ("customer"."c_mktsegment" IN ('BUILDING', 'FURNITURE', 'AUTOMOBILE') OR ("customer"."c_mktsegment" IN ('BUILDING') AND "customer"."c_mktsegment" = 'AUTOMOBILE')) AND "lineorder"."lo_revenue" BETWEEN 3234215 AND 4271106 GROUP BY "customer"."c_mktsegment", "lineorder"."lo_quantity" ORDER BY "customer"."c_mktsegment", "lineorder"."lo_quantity";

SELECT avg("lineorder"."lo_partkey") as agg_0, min("lineorder"."lo_orderkey" + "lineorder"."lo_ordertotalprice") as agg_1 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "lineorder"."lo_custkey"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_city" AS varchar) LIKE '%VIETNAM%' AND CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%REG%' AND CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) LIKE '%MACHINER%Y%' AND CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%MACHINERY%' AND CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) LIKE '%EAST%';

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_suppkey", max("lineorder"."lo_supplycost") as agg_0 FROM "part" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "lineorder"."lo_partkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "supplier" ON "lineorder"."lo_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey"  WHERE CAST("part"."p_color" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%g%host%' AND "lineorder"."lo_tax" = 8 AND CAST("supplier"."s_city" AS varchar) LIKE '%SAU%DI%' GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_suppkey" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_suppkey";

SELECT min("lineorder"."lo_commitdate" + "lineorder"."lo_partkey") as agg_0 FROM "lineorder" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "lineorder"."lo_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"  WHERE "lineorder"."lo_shipmode" != 'REG AIR';

SELECT min("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0, sum("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_1 FROM "customer"  WHERE "customer"."c_nation" IN ('IRAN', 'INDIA', 'EGYPT', 'CANADA', 'KENYA', 'FRANCE', 'RUSSIA', 'JORDAN', 'UNITED KINGDOM', 'PERU', 'MOROCCO', 'CHINA', 'ROMANIA', 'INDONESIA', 'UNITED STATES', 'ARGENTINA', 'BRAZIL', 'VIETNAM', 'MOZAMBIQUE', 'SAUDI ARABIA', 'IRAQ', 'ALGERIA') AND CAST("customer"."c_city" AS varchar) LIKE '%ROMANIA%' AND CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) LIKE '%MACHINERY%' AND "customer"."c_nation" != 'PERU';

SELECT avg("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0 FROM "customer"  WHERE (CAST("customer"."c_city" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%GERMANY%' OR ("customer"."c_custkey" <= 38952 AND "customer"."c_city" != 'RUSSIA   4')) AND CAST("customer"."c_nation" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%RU%SSIA%' AND "customer"."c_mktsegment" IN ('BUILDING', 'HOUSEHOLD', 'FURNITURE', 'AUTOMOBILE') AND CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%MIDDLE%' AND CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) LIKE '%AMERICA%';

SELECT "customer"."c_city", min("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0, min("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_1, max("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_2 FROM "customer"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%FURNITURE%' AND CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%BUILDING%' AND "customer"."c_nation" IN ('ALGERIA', 'SAUDI ARABIA', 'UNITED KINGDOM', 'VIETNAM', 'KENYA', 'GERMANY', 'ARGENTINA', 'UNITED STATES', 'INDIA', 'BRAZIL', 'MOROCCO', 'ETHIOPIA', 'JORDAN', 'PERU', 'JAPAN', 'FRANCE', 'CHINA') AND CAST("customer"."c_city" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%GERMAN%Y%' GROUP BY "customer"."c_city" ORDER BY "customer"."c_city";

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_discount", "lineorder"."lo_orderdate", sum("lineorder"."lo_linenumber" + "lineorder"."lo_discount") as agg_0, max("lineorder"."lo_revenue") as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM "part" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "lineorder"."lo_partkey"  WHERE (CAST("lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" AS varchar) LIKE '%5%-LOW%' OR "lineorder"."lo_shipmode" IN ('FOB', 'TRUCK', 'SHIP', 'REG AIR', 'AIR') OR CAST("lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%SPECIFI%ED%') AND "lineorder"."lo_commitdate" <= 19926161 AND "lineorder"."lo_discount" BETWEEN 2 AND 7 AND ("lineorder"."lo_extendedprice" >= 4924398 OR ("lineorder"."lo_extendedprice" >= 1297128 AND "lineorder"."lo_extendedprice" >= 4754710)) GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_discount", "lineorder"."lo_orderdate" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_discount", "lineorder"."lo_orderdate";

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_shippriority", "lineorder"."lo_suppkey", avg("lineorder"."lo_extendedprice") as agg_0 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "lineorder"."lo_custkey"  WHERE ("customer"."c_mktsegment" IN ('BUILDING', 'AUTOMOBILE') OR CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) LIKE '%MACHINERY%' OR CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%HOUSEHOLD%') AND CAST("lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" AS varchar) LIKE '%SPEC%IFIED%' AND CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%E%AST%' AND CAST("customer"."c_nation" AS varchar) LIKE '%BRAZ%IL%' GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_shippriority", "lineorder"."lo_suppkey" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_shippriority", "lineorder"."lo_suppkey";

SELECT sum("lineorder"."lo_quantity") as agg_0, max("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM "part" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "lineorder"."lo_partkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "lineorder"."lo_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"  WHERE "customer"."c_mktsegment" IN ('HOUSEHOLD', 'FURNITURE', 'AUTOMOBILE', 'MACHINERY') AND "part"."p_name" = 'yellow medium' AND "lineorder"."lo_supplycost" <= 72433;

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_commitdate", "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "lineorder"."lo_custkey"  WHERE "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" IN ('1-URGENT', '5-LOW', '3-MEDIUM', '2-HIGH') AND "lineorder"."lo_shipmode" IN ('RAIL', 'MAIL') AND (CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) LIKE '%ASI%A%' OR CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) LIKE '%AMERICA%') GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_commitdate", "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_commitdate", "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority";

SELECT sum("part"."p_partkey" + "part"."p_size") as agg_0, sum("part"."p_partkey" + "part"."p_size") as agg_1, max("part"."p_size" + "part"."p_partkey") as agg_2 FROM "part"  WHERE "part"."p_color" IN ('dodger', 'snow', 'sandy', 'thistle', 'tomato', 'lace', 'metallic', 'pale', 'rosy', 'spring', 'lavender', 'cyan', 'ivory') AND CAST("part"."p_category" AS varchar) LIKE '%MFG%R#51%';

SELECT sum("lineorder"."lo_ordertotalprice") as agg_0 FROM "part" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "lineorder"."lo_partkey"  WHERE CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) LIKE '%AIR%' AND "lineorder"."lo_linenumber" != 6;

SELECT sum("lineorder"."lo_revenue") as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM "lineorder"  WHERE ("lineorder"."lo_tax" >= 7 OR "lineorder"."lo_tax" BETWEEN 4 AND 5) AND CAST("lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" AS varchar) LIKE '%3-MEDIUM%';

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_suppkey", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "lineorder"."lo_custkey"  WHERE CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%AIR%' AND "lineorder"."lo_revenue" >= 7396607 AND "customer"."c_nation" IN ('MOROCCO', 'CANADA', 'JAPAN', 'ROMANIA', 'ARGENTINA', 'INDONESIA', 'ETHIOPIA', 'PERU', 'IRAN', 'SAUDI ARABIA', 'RUSSIA', 'KENYA') AND CAST("customer"."c_city" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%IRAN%' AND "customer"."c_region" IN ('MIDDLE EAST', 'EUROPE', 'AMERICA') GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_suppkey" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_suppkey";

SELECT "customer"."c_mktsegment", min("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0, max("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_1 FROM "customer"  WHERE "customer"."c_nation" IN ('ROMANIA', 'CANADA', 'UNITED STATES', 'MOROCCO', 'JAPAN', 'CHINA', 'IRAN', 'FRANCE', 'SAUDI ARABIA', 'PERU', 'MOZAMBIQUE', 'INDIA', 'IRAQ', 'JORDAN') GROUP BY "customer"."c_mktsegment" ORDER BY "customer"."c_mktsegment";

SELECT avg("lineorder"."lo_partkey" + "lineorder"."lo_suppkey") as agg_0, avg("lineorder"."lo_revenue" + "lineorder"."lo_linenumber") as agg_1 FROM "lineorder" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "lineorder"."lo_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"  WHERE CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) LIKE '%MA%IL%' AND ("lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" = '4-NOT SPECIFIED' OR "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" IN ('3-MEDIUM', '2-HIGH', '4-NOT SPECIFIED', '5-LOW'));

SELECT "customer"."c_nation", "lineorder"."lo_quantity", sum("lineorder"."lo_shippriority" + "lineorder"."lo_partkey") as agg_0, avg("lineorder"."lo_shippriority") as agg_1, avg("lineorder"."lo_orderkey") as agg_2 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "lineorder"."lo_custkey"  WHERE ("lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" != '5-LOW' OR "lineorder"."lo_supplycost" BETWEEN 88663 AND 91671 OR CAST("lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%5-L%OW%') AND CAST("lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" AS varchar) LIKE '%3-MEDIUM%' GROUP BY "customer"."c_nation", "lineorder"."lo_quantity" ORDER BY "customer"."c_nation", "lineorder"."lo_quantity";

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority", "lineorder"."lo_orderdate", COUNT(*) as agg_0, sum("lineorder"."lo_extendedprice" + "lineorder"."lo_discount") as agg_1, sum("lineorder"."lo_tax" + "lineorder"."lo_ordertotalprice") as agg_2 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "lineorder"."lo_custkey"  WHERE (CAST("lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" AS varchar) LIKE '%4-NOT%' OR "lineorder"."lo_partkey" BETWEEN 41248 AND 58200 OR "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" IN ('2-HIGH', '4-NOT SPECIFIED', '1-URGENT')) AND ("customer"."c_nation" != 'BRAZIL' OR "customer"."c_nation" IN ('PERU', 'UNITED KINGDOM', 'CANADA', 'BRAZIL', 'ARGENTINA', 'MOZAMBIQUE', 'EGYPT', 'IRAQ', 'RUSSIA', 'CHINA', 'JORDAN', 'UNITED STATES', 'INDIA') OR "customer"."c_nation" IN ('SAUDI ARABIA', 'ALGERIA')) AND "lineorder"."lo_custkey" >= 35525 AND "customer"."c_custkey" <= 44840 GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority", "lineorder"."lo_orderdate" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority", "lineorder"."lo_orderdate";

SELECT "supplier"."s_address", "supplier"."s_city", max("supplier"."s_suppkey") as agg_0 FROM "supplier"  WHERE CAST("supplier"."s_nation" AS varchar) LIKE '%PERU%' AND "supplier"."s_region" != 'ASIA' AND ("supplier"."s_suppkey" <= 945 OR "supplier"."s_name" = 'Supplier#000003969') AND CAST("supplier"."s_city" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%ROM%ANIA%' GROUP BY "supplier"."s_address", "supplier"."s_city" ORDER BY "supplier"."s_address", "supplier"."s_city";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0, max("part"."p_partkey") as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM "part"  WHERE "part"."p_category" IN ('MFGR#53', 'MFGR#21', 'MFGR#45', 'MFGR#52', 'MFGR#55') AND CAST("part"."p_name" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%sky%' AND "part"."p_container" IN ('SM PKG', 'SM BAG', 'JUMBO PACK') AND CAST("part"."p_color" AS varchar) LIKE '%o%range%' AND "part"."p_type" != 'STANDARD BRUSHED COPPER';

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_linenumber", sum("lineorder"."lo_suppkey" + "lineorder"."lo_tax") as agg_0, min("lineorder"."lo_orderdate") as agg_1 FROM "supplier" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "lineorder"."lo_suppkey"  WHERE "supplier"."s_city" IN ('JORDAN   7', 'CANADA   8', 'MOROCCO  8', 'IRAQ     9', 'IRAQ     8', 'PERU     1', 'JORDAN   6', 'KENYA    0', 'KENYA    3', 'FRANCE   9', 'UNITED ST8', 'ARGENTINA1', 'MOZAMBIQU5', 'PERU     7', 'ETHIOPIA 1', 'IRAN     3', 'FRANCE   7', 'KENYA    4', 'GERMANY  2', 'UNITED KI5', 'CHINA    5', 'EGYPT    3', 'ETHIOPIA 0') AND "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" = '2-HIGH' AND CAST("lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%3-MEDIUM%' GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_linenumber" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_linenumber";

SELECT "part"."p_name", avg("part"."p_partkey") as agg_0 FROM "part"  WHERE CAST("part"."p_mfgr" AS varchar) LIKE '%MF%GR#1%' AND CAST("part"."p_type" AS varchar) LIKE '%BRA%SS%' AND "part"."p_color" IN ('metallic', 'honeydew', 'steel', 'cornflower', 'salmon', 'seashell', 'moccasin', 'antique', 'ghost', 'green', 'orange', 'purple', 'coral', 'snow', 'violet', 'saddle', 'rosy', 'sky', 'dodger', 'chiffon', 'bisque', 'lemon', 'grey', 'yellow', 'aquamarine', 'pink', 'sandy', 'cornsilk', 'beige', 'blanched', 'slate', 'burnished', 'cyan', 'indian', 'thistle') AND CAST("part"."p_container" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%CAN%' GROUP BY "part"."p_name" ORDER BY "part"."p_name";
SELECT sum("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0 FROM "customer"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%AMERICA%';

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_shippriority", sum("lineorder"."lo_linenumber" + "lineorder"."lo_extendedprice") as agg_0, max("lineorder"."lo_tax") as agg_1 FROM "supplier" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "lineorder"."lo_suppkey"  WHERE CAST("lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" AS varchar) LIKE '%3-ME%DIUM%' GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_shippriority" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_shippriority";

SELECT "customer"."c_region", max("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0, sum("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM "customer"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_nation" AS varchar) LIKE '%KENYA%' AND CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%FURNIT%URE%' AND CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%AUTOMOBILE%' AND "customer"."c_custkey" BETWEEN 20556 AND 52220 AND CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%AFRICA%' GROUP BY "customer"."c_region" ORDER BY "customer"."c_region";

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_tax", COUNT(*) as agg_0, sum("lineorder"."lo_quantity" + "lineorder"."lo_custkey") as agg_1 FROM "lineorder"  WHERE "lineorder"."lo_shipmode" IN ('SHIP', 'TRUCK', 'RAIL', 'AIR', 'REG AIR') AND "lineorder"."lo_custkey" BETWEEN 23583 AND 59964 AND CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) LIKE '%SHIP%' AND "lineorder"."lo_tax" <= 0 GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_tax" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_tax";

SELECT "supplier"."s_nation", COUNT(*) as agg_0, min("lineorder"."lo_orderkey") as agg_1, min("lineorder"."lo_orderdate" + "lineorder"."lo_suppkey") as agg_2 FROM "lineorder" LEFT OUTER JOIN "supplier" ON "lineorder"."lo_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "part" ON "lineorder"."lo_partkey" = "part"."p_partkey"  WHERE (CAST("supplier"."s_nation" AS varchar) LIKE '%JORDAN%' OR (CAST("supplier"."s_nation" AS varchar) LIKE '%R%USSIA%' AND CAST("supplier"."s_nation" AS varchar) LIKE '%KINGDOM%')) AND CAST("part"."p_color" AS varchar) LIKE '%chocolate%' AND "lineorder"."lo_shippriority" != 0 GROUP BY "supplier"."s_nation" ORDER BY "supplier"."s_nation";

SELECT "customer"."c_nation", COUNT(*) as agg_0, sum("customer"."c_custkey" + "lineorder"."lo_shippriority") as agg_1 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "lineorder"."lo_custkey"  WHERE ("customer"."c_mktsegment" IN ('BUILDING', 'FURNITURE', 'HOUSEHOLD', 'MACHINERY') OR "customer"."c_mktsegment" IN ('HOUSEHOLD', 'MACHINERY', 'FURNITURE', 'AUTOMOBILE')) AND CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) LIKE '%FOB%' AND CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) LIKE '%MID%DLE%' AND CAST("customer"."c_nation" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%ROMANIA%' GROUP BY "customer"."c_nation" ORDER BY "customer"."c_nation";

SELECT "supplier"."s_nation", min("lineorder"."lo_suppkey" + "lineorder"."lo_orderkey") as agg_0, min("lineorder"."lo_extendedprice" + "lineorder"."lo_linenumber") as agg_1 FROM "supplier" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "lineorder"."lo_suppkey"  WHERE CAST("supplier"."s_city" AS varchar) LIKE '%U%NITED%' AND CAST("supplier"."s_nation" AS varchar) LIKE '%U%NITED%' AND "lineorder"."lo_extendedprice" >= 10306472 AND CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%RAIL%' GROUP BY "supplier"."s_nation" ORDER BY "supplier"."s_nation";
